{
  "stem": "1917.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I would have never, ever dared disobey their orders.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was a very good, obedient child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my father said to me, you are so stupid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You are so stubborn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You never seem to understand it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It doesn't get into your head that there is nothing we can do about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We just have to learn to take it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I felt like I was cooped in an elevator that was burning, and there was no way out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was-- I was trapped inside, and there was nothing I could do about it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this is what happened to me in 1967 in Terre Haute when the house was surrounded by-- by young kids who were playing all kinds of tricks on me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And again, emotionally, there was nothing I could do about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "If I went out to chase them, they came back with reinforcement.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And emotionally, it threw me back to 1943.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so in 1944-- winter of '43 and '44, my mother became very ill.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In the meantime, there were all kinds of other laws were coming.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And by beginning of '43 [SOBS] we had to let-- we had two maids who were helping my mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we had three families who worked with my father on the farm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We had a quarter for the servants who were working on the farm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And Jews could not hire anybody who was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So we let-- we had to let them go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And my father tried to work as much of the farm as he could.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we helped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We help with around the farm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We knew how to raise vegetables and water, get water from the well, pull it up, and water the garden.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
